# Implementation Plan - Fix Encoding Issues (Mojibake)

The project suffers from widespread encoding issues ("Mojibake") where UTF-8 characters are interpreted as Windows-1252, resulting in garbled text (e.g., "SystÃ¨me" instead of "Système"). This affects the VBA source files and consequently the User Interface.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> This operation modifies multiple files in `vba-files`. A backup is recommended, although the script detects changes before writing.

## Proposed Changes
### Global
- Run [scripts/fix-mojibake.ps1](file:///c:/VBA/SGQ%201.65/scripts/fix-mojibake.ps1) on the entire `vba-files` directory.
